      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 35 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 35 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>晉，康侯用錫馬蕃庶，晝日三接。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In Jin we see a prince who secures the tranquillity (of the people) presented on that account with numerous horses (by the king), and three times in a day received at interviews.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="yijing-035-jin__alignment-002">
