      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 35 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 35 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：晉如，摧如，貞吉。罔孚，裕无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows one wishing to advance, and (at the same time) kept back. Let him be firm and correct, and there will be good fortune. If trust be not reposed in him, let him maintain a large and generous mind, and there will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
