      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 35 六三</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>六三：眾允，悔亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The third SIX, divided, shows its subject trusted by all (around him). All occasion for repentance will disappear.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
