      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 35 九四</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 35 九四</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九四：晉如碩鼠，貞厲。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fourth NINE, undivided, shows its subject with the appearance of advancing, but like a marmot. However firm and correct he may be, the position is one of peril.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
